org.dspace.sword2

Interface SwordContentIngester

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractSwordContentIngester, BinaryContentIngester, SimpleZipContentIngester, SwordMETSContentIngester

    public interface SwordContentIngester
    Interface behind which can be implemented ingest mechanisms for SWORD deposit requests. Instances of this class should be obtained via the SwordIngesterFactory class.
    Author:
    Richard Jones
